{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
# /user-story — User Story

## Uso
```
/user-story [descricao]
```

## Fases

### Fase 0 — Reconhecimento
1. Ler historias existentes em `{{paths.docsRoot}}/po/` para entender o padrao
2. Identificar personas do projeto
3. Verificar features relacionadas

### Fase 1 — Criar User Story

Salvar em: `{{paths.docsRoot}}/po/user-stories/{id}-{titulo-kebab-case}.md`

```markdown
# {ID}: {Titulo}

**Tipo**: Feature | Bug Fix | Melhoria
**Modulo(s)**: {modulos afetados}
**Prioridade**: Must | Should | Could

## Historia

**Como** {persona},
**Quero** {acao desejada},
**Para** {beneficio/objetivo}.

## Criterios de Aceitacao

### Cenario 1: {caminho feliz}
**Dado** que {pre-condicao}
**Quando** {acao}
**Entao** {resultado}

### Cenario 2: {caminho alternativo}
**Dado** que {pre-condicao}
**Quando** {acao}
**Entao** {resultado}

### Cenario 3: {tratamento de erro}
**Dado** que {pre-condicao}
**Quando** {acao invalida}
**Entao** {mensagem de erro}

## Notas Tecnicas
- **Componentes**: {componentes afetados}
- **API**: {endpoints necessarios}
- **Dependencias**: {dependencias de outros modulos}

## Estimativa
- **Complexidade**: P | M | G
- **Story Points**: 1 | 2 | 3 | 5 | 8 | 13
```

## Checklist
- [ ] Persona identificada
- [ ] Beneficio claro (nao apenas a acao)
- [ ] Criterios de aceitacao testaveis
- [ ] Cenario de erro incluido
- [ ] Estimativa de complexidade
{{else}}
# /user-story — User Story

## Usage
```
/user-story [description]
```

## Phases

### Phase 0 — Reconnaissance
1. Read existing stories in `{{paths.docsRoot}}/po/` to understand the pattern
2. Identify project personas
3. Check related features

### Phase 1 — Create User Story

Save to: `{{paths.docsRoot}}/po/user-stories/{id}-{title-kebab-case}.md`

```markdown
# {ID}: {Title}

**Type**: Feature | Bug Fix | Enhancement
**Module(s)**: {affected modules}
**Priority**: Must | Should | Could

## Story

**As a** {persona},
**I want** {desired action},
**So that** {benefit/goal}.

## Acceptance Criteria

### Scenario 1: {happy path}
**Given** {precondition}
**When** {action}
**Then** {result}

### Scenario 2: {alternative path}
**Given** {precondition}
**When** {action}
**Then** {result}

### Scenario 3: {error handling}
**Given** {precondition}
**When** {invalid action}
**Then** {error message}

## Technical Notes
- **Components**: {affected components}
- **API**: {required endpoints}
- **Dependencies**: {dependencies on other modules}

## Estimation
- **Complexity**: S | M | L
- **Story Points**: 1 | 2 | 3 | 5 | 8 | 13
```

## Checklist
- [ ] Persona identified
- [ ] Clear benefit (not just the action)
- [ ] Testable acceptance criteria
- [ ] Error scenario included
- [ ] Complexity estimation
{{/if}}
